    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's ready for its next chapter! This vehicle has been a reliable companion and still has plenty of life left in it. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a solid choice for anyone looking for a functional and affordable car. It's the perfect opportunity to own a well-loved vehicle that gets the job done!",
